                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">
              Ready to Find Plans in Your Area?
            </h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Enter your ZIP code to see all available plans, real rates, and start comparing electricity providers in your specific area.
