            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-texas-navy mb-6 group-hover:text-texas-red transition-colors">Real Rates Only</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              No <strong class="text-texas-red">"teaser rates"</strong> that jump after 3 months. Every rate includes all taxes, fees, and charges so you know exactly what you'll pay.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-texas-gold transition-all duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-texas-gold/10 to-texas-gold/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:from-texas-gold/20 group-hover:to-texas-gold/30 transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-texas-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
