            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-texas-navy transition-all duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-texas-navy/10 to-texas-navy/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:from-texas-navy/20 group-hover:to-texas-navy/30 transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-texas-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
