              Need Expert Guidance?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
              Texas electricity is <strong class="text-texas-red">intentionally complicated.</strong> Get honest guidance from our energy experts who won't try to sell you anything.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
              <Button variant="texas-primary" size="lg" className="h-16 px-12 text-lg font-bold rounded-xl">
                <svg class="mr-3 w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
